      dd
        p A: aassio’s plan for the distribution of the billion tokens issued initially is:
        ul
          li 50% will be sold in 1st and 2nd token sales
          li 35% will be reserved for the company and shareholders with a 4-year-lockup & vesting programme
          li 10% reserved for the Team Pool
          li 4% reserved for Advisor & Affiliate Pool (A&A Pool)
