      dd A: Presale - 1 ETH; Public sale - no minimum

      dt Q: What is the total token supply?
      dd A: Total token supply = 1,000,000,000 = One billion

      dt Q: Is there a lock-in period or vesting schedule for the share of tokens to the team?
      dd A: Yes, our team’s token holdings are locked in for a minimum of 6 months, with an 4 year vesting period.

      dt Q: How do I qualify to buy tokens?
      dd A: Qualifying to buy tokens is easy. Simply sign up on the website and follow the Know Your Customer instructions.To buy tokens you must successfully complete the KYC and AML process on our website.

      dt Q: What countries are forbidden from participating in the token sale?
      dd A: Sadly, we cannot officially sell to residents of the USA, Afghanistan, Bosnia & Herzegovina, Burundi, Central African Republic, Democratic Republic of the Congo, Egypt, Eritrea, Ethiopia, Guinea, Guinea-Bissau, Haiti, Iran, Iraq, Lebanon, Libya, Maldives, Mali, Moldova, Montenegro, Myanmar, North Korea, Pakistan, Serbia, Somalia, Sri Lanka, Sudan, Syria, Trinidad and Tobago, Tunisia, Venezuela, Yemen and Zimbabwe. Email us at #{mail_to 'rf@aass.io'} for additional possible options.

      dt Q: Do you have a referral program?
      dd A: Yes! We encourage referrals and details our referral program and airdrop program can be found on our website, #{link_to 'aass.io', 'https://aass.io/', target: '_blank'}.

      dt Q: When will the token be available on exchanges?
      dd A: We will release information on this at the appropriate juncture, following completion of our token sale

      h3.mt-5.mb-5 Purchasing Tokens

      dt Q: How do I join the whitelist?
      dd A: Register on our Private Sale page for access to our whitelist

      dt Q:Can I participate with fiat or other cryptocurrencies?
      dd A: Currently, we are only accepting ETH contributions. However, there are many tools to turn other cryptocurrencies into ETH such as #{link_to 'shapeshift.io', 'https://shapeshift.io/', target: '_blank'}

      dt Q: How do I know if my token purchase has been confirmed?
      dd
        p A: The status of your token purchase transaction can be found on the blockchain explorer. You will also be able to see the token balance reflected in your Ether wallet if you add the AAS token to it.
        p = link_to 'Instructions for adding custom tokens for myetherwallet.com', 'https://myetherwallet.github.io/knowledge-base/send/adding-new-token-and-sending-custom-tokens.html', target: '_blank'

      dt Q: Can I buy tokens multiple times during the token sale?
      dd A: Yes, we are not restricting purchases for those who wish to capitalise on our bonus structure

      dt Q: How will the coins be distributed?
      dd A: The token will be distributed via a sales smart contract and the current rate of ETH to token will be displayed on your investor portal during different stages of the sale. To purchase the token, all you have to do is to send ETH from a wallet that you control to the sales contract address, which will also be displayed in the investor portal. The tokens will be sent to the purchasing wallet automatically.

      dt Q: Can I use MEW/Metamask/ImToken/Ledger to receive my tokens?
      dd A: Yes as long as it is an ERC20 compatible wallet.

      dt Q: What are examples of ERC20 compatible wallets?
      dd
        p A: Any wallet compatible with ETH is also compatible with ERC20 tokens. However, you should NOT purchase tokens directly from an exchange wallet (Coinbase, Binance etc). An exchange wallet is managed by the exchange, and you do not have direct access to it. If you purchase tokens from an exchange wallet, you will not be able to access the tokens. Here is a list of recommended wallets:
        ul
          li MyEtherWallet (no download needed)
          li MetaMask (Firefox and Chrome browser addon)
          li Mist (Desktop)
          li Parity (Desktop)
          li imToken (Mobile)
          li Trust(Mobile)
          li Cipher(Mobile)

      dt Q:Can I send ETH directly from an exchange?
      dd A: No, please see above.


      dt Q: What if I only have an exchange ETH wallet?
      dd A: You should create an actual ETH wallet. Follow the instructions at #{link_to 'myetherwallet.com', 'https://www.myetherwallet.com/', target: '_blank'}. The process is really quick and easy, and should only take a couple of minutes.

      dt Q: How much gas should I set for ETH payment?
      dd A: We recommend sending at least 100,000 gas with your transaction. Don't worry, any gas that's not used to run the token purchase function will be refunded to your wallet.

      dt Q: Are bonuses based on the time when I submitted the investment form or when I made the payment?
      dd A: We will burn any unsold tokens

      dt Q: When will the KYC/AML take place?
      dd A: Immediately upon registration for purchase

      dt Q: Where is the whitepaper/pitch deck for the token sale?
      dd A: Available for download at #{link_to 'aass.io', 'https://aass.io/', target: '_blank'}

      dt Q: Do you have a white paper in other languages?
      dd A: Yes, our whitepaper is available in English, Russian, and Chinese, although we ask that anyone reading the translated versions excuse any discrepancies in translation and the native English (U.S.) version remains the final edit superseding all other versions

      dt Q: Do you have a bounty program?
      dd A: Yes! Find it #{link_to 'HERE', 'https://bitcointalk.org/index.php?topic=5058735.0', target: '_blank'}.

      dt Q: How and when will I receive my bounty tokens?
      dd A: We will open source our smart contracts on Github. Any user is encouraged to exam the codebase and look for bugs and vulnerabilities. Bounty rewards will be based on the severity of the issue. Rewards will be given on a first come first serve basis. Issues that are already submitted by another user, or already known to the team will not eligible for the bounty.

      h3.mt-5.mb-5 Token Details

      dt Q: Are the tokens minable?
      dd A: Yes, new tokens will be minted with new properties added to the network and will be burned.

      dt Q: After each real estate tokenization (RET), new AAS tokens are minted. Will the increase of total number of AAS tokens lead to a decrease in the value of a single AAS token?
      dd A: When more AAS are mined, don’t forget, the value of the aassio ecosystem (aassioECO) as a whole also increases proportionately.  For example, a new property valued $500K after RET has successfully become part of the aassioECO. aassioECO has just grown by $500K, meanwhile, the value of newly mined AAS will exactly add up to $500K.

      dt Q: Are the tokens ERC20 tokens?
      dd A: Yes, they are fully ERC20 compatible.

      dt Q: What are the details of the token if I want to add it to my wallet?
      dd A: We will release this information at the beginning of the sale, please stay tuned.

      dt Q: Are you going to audit the token’s smart contract?
      dd A: Yes, our token smart contracts has already been audited by security professionals to identify any potential issues.

      dt Q: What is the official contract address for the token?
      dd A: We will release this information at the beginning of the sale, please stay tuned


